abstract: >-
  DevVerse CS Blog is a comprehensive technical blog platform featuring over 40 in-depth articles
  covering Software Engineering, Web Development, Artificial Intelligence, Machine Learning, Cloud
  Computing, and Computer Science fundamentals. Built with Next.js 15, React 18, and MDX, it offers
  a modern reading experience with dark mode support, RSS/Atom feeds, user authentication via Supabase,
  article favorites system, and responsive design. The platform features technical deep-dives on topics
  including Graph Neural Networks, Agentic AI systems, microservices architecture, WebAssembly, quantum
  computing, and modern web frameworks. Each article combines theoretical foundations with practical
  code examples, making complex topics accessible to developers at all levels. The blog serves as both
  an educational resource and a reference for modern software development practices.
